## Description {#details}

Generic tagged DWARF-like metadata node.

An un-specialized DWARF-like metadata node. The first operand is a (possibly empty) null-separated <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdstring">MDString</a></em> header that contains arbitrary fields. The remaining operands are <em><a href="#acca183c390d40cddeec0646c7f54df63">dwarf&#95;operands()</a></em>, and are pointers to other metadata.

Uses the SubclassData32 <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/metadata">Metadata</a> slot.

Definition at line 236 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/debuginfometadata-h">DebugInfoMetadata.h</a>.
